>I may have been unclear in what I wrote earlier.  I want the screen to 
>clear as soon as a response is registered. The program is recording 
>reaction time and voice recordings just fine.  The problem is that the 
>first two segments are 5 seconds each, but if the subject answers 2s after 
>problem onset, the screen doesn't clear for 8 more seconds (i.e. until the 
>very beginning of the final segment).
